value: 5065 - Electronic Parts and Equipment, Not Elsewhere Classified Summary > SAGEMCOM AUSTRALASIA PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover electronic parts and equipment, not elsewhere classified. The company is involved in the import and export of goods. SAGEMCOM AUSTRALASIA PTY LTD is headquartered in Sydney, New South Wales. It is headed by director & company secretary Susan Gai Strouthos. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $32.03 million. Its net profit totalled $729,000. SAGEMCOM AUSTRALASIA PTY LTD forms part of the wholesale trade industry sector.
